<plot>Chloe is a teacher. She is also a divorced mother with two children,who believes she has found love again when she meets Educational Psychologist Dan. Dan does his best to build good relationships with Chloe's daughters, Lucy 6 and Alice 14 and moves in with Chloe. Everything seems perfect until the police come to arrest Dan. A six year old girl he has been assessing claims he has sexually abused her. Chloe loves Dan, but can she still trust him? What happened when he was alone with her children? Chloe sets out to find the truth and discover a way through the conflicting evidence.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?346073</url></doc>
